{"tid":2385665,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"如果林過雲是警察 - 高慧然","createTime":"2021-01-29T07:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T10:52:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5a2f43cacf5a4665efba2128c4d6bf21cd33c6c6","tid":2385665,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:16:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210129/AYSWVRO2EFAVJP5ZCQ7LIG6VBQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210129%2FAYSWVRO2EFAVJP5ZCQ7LIG6VBQ%2F&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w2E7lpprR278wgWha8tNVfY%3D&h=f8fa67c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210129%2FAYSWVRO2EFAVJP5ZCQ7LIG6VBQ%2F&h=9e230c60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210129/AYSWVRO2EFAVJP5ZCQ7LIG6VBQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n如果林過雲是警察 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kcVFGq1yzexl2BIC37R4aMKYGFc=/1246x866/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TGVMSBMBBNC5TM3LNKC7EAURS4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkcVFGq1yzexl2BIC37R4aMKYGFc%3D%2F1246x866%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTGVMSBMBBNC5TM3LNKC7EAURS4.png&h=c42c85e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n毒品調查科探員猥褻、非禮及與未成年女童非法性交罪名成立，被判監46個月。涉案女童多達6名，年齡最小的僅11歲，最大的也不過是14歲。不知在今日的香港法庭，「非法性交」是甚麼定義？成年男性跟未成年女性性交，根本不存在合法與非法之別，即使不是強姦，起碼都是誘姦。不知護苗基金認為判決是否合理？是不是選擇性護苗，對被香港警察摧折的幼苗沒有感覺？<br />\n<br />\n有網民把另一宗性侵案放上網絡進行對比，去年5月，24歲地盤工性侵三個女網友，獲刑12年。與去年的同類型案例相比，警員犯案，與地盤工犯案，性質一樣，但後果截然不同。很明顯，警察獲得輕判。而事實是，論年齡，警察侵犯的女童年齡更小；論人數，警察侵犯的女童人數是地盤工的2倍。理論上，執法人員知法犯法，理應比普通巿民犯法受到更嚴厲的法律制裁，事實卻相反，警察犯下比地盤工嚴重得多的罪行，獲刑卻短得多，不到地盤工獲刑的三分一年期。<br />\n<br />\n有誰能解釋兩宗罪案，為甚麼其中一個罪犯承擔的法律後果輕得多呢？唯一的原因是他的職業身份嗎？在今日香港，香港警察已經成為在法律上擁有特別豁免權的特權階層嗎？<br />\n<br />\n林過雲真是生不逢時，他若在今日香港擔任警察，命運必定改寫。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook：kowaiyin.yoyoko"},{"pid":"1957088e4e5bdf642afcfbf54df6f6aa09d4d176","tid":2385665,"uid":239392,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:25:47.000Z","msg":"警察犯法扣減四分三刑期，呢個係福利呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d549b3c2e01e9d360e8c59ab6ffaeaf75e1755","tid":2385665,"uid":30988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:29:01.000Z","msg":"賤賊﹕我們都是林過雲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703d762ddf80b1cea29942f2bd457862acd48c56","tid":2385665,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:39:13.000Z","msg":"如果依家出多個林過雲,啲黑警對佢實溫柔過後生仔."},{"pid":"dcf718ea63e9c31a6e3b4a22710a4f472791d6e4","tid":2385665,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"703d762ddf80b1cea29942f2bd457862acd48c56","tid":2385665,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:39:13.000Z","msg":"如果依家出多個林過雲,啲黑警對佢實溫柔過後生仔."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:47:20.000Z","msg":"陳同佳已經係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0503ba6e34e5d9ae135865f5211ef19d26e64e","tid":2385665,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ff0bfab26ab51b31536a15df1c3bd70d5324ba","tid":2385665,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcf718ea63e9c31a6e3b4a22710a4f472791d6e4","tid":2385665,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"703d762ddf80b1cea29942f2bd457862acd48c56","tid":2385665,"uid":143241,"like":0,